name: It is raining "I"s
description:
Left and Right Arrows to move.

Online Leader board works in the scratch website. Not here because I don't own a server.

As a purple square you are dodging the falling "I"s from outer space. While collecting health packs to keep your health up. You can also collect some speed boost. This game was made in 72 hours for the Zeno Game Jam. Made in scratch so click the buttons on the top right to start and stop. Scratch project link: It is raining "I"s on Scratch (mit.edu)
